<div id="split">
	<p>Tap on the items you want to pay for.  If multiple people tap on the same item, its cost will be shared evenly.</p>
	<p>Once <strong>everyone</strong> is done picking their items, click the "confirm" button at the bottom.</p>
	<ul class="items">{{items}}</ul>
	<a class="confirm">Split</a>
	<a class="cancel">Cancel</a>
</div>
